  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Analysis
    Incremental compilation analysis interface.

    SBT incremental compilation analysis processor interface.
    Compiler
    SBT compiler interface.
    CompilerLogger
    Logger providing compilation feedback.
    SourcePosition
    Compilation error/warning position.
    SourcePositionMapper
